<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract This article serves to witness the life and works of Balduíno Rambo, and his contribution to the the first clays of Anthropology at the Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul. Our material considers the origin, intellectual formation, personality, and activities of this thinker, situating his contributions to diverse fields of knowledge within the context of his time.]]></p></abstract>
